panels.content:
# Throughput-terminal Trends

This dashboard display an overview of how throughput changes over terminal numbers. Feel free to mix and match, but be warned the charts can get overwhelming pretty fast.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT DISTINCT ON (terminals)
	time, 
	CAST(terminals AS TEXT) as metric,
  CAST(metrics->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION) as value
FROM oltpbench_results
WHERE 
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
  benchmark_type = ${benchmark_type} AND
  client_time = 60 AND
  git_branch = 'master'
ORDER BY terminals, time desc;

SELECT DISTINCT ON (terminals)
   CAST(metrics->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION) as throughput,
   expect_throughput,
   CAST(metrics->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION)-expect_throughput as diff_throughput
FROM oltpbench_results
CROSS JOIN (
	SELECT (${terminals})*CAST(metrics->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION) as expect_throughput
		FROM oltpbench_results
	WHERE
	   benchmark_type = ${benchmark_type}
	   AND terminals = 1 AND
	   client_time = 60 AND
	   git_branch = 'master'
	 GROUP BY time, benchmark_type, terminals, metrics->>'throughput'
	 ORDER BY time desc
	 LIMIT 1
) AS base
WHERE
   benchmark_type = ${benchmark_type} AND
   terminals = (${terminals}) AND
   client_time = 60 AND
   git_branch = 'master'
ORDER BY terminals, time desc;

SELECT DISTINCT ON (terminals)
